<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Reset Password - Tabster</title>
<style>
  body {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #e0f7ff, #f5faff 60%);
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .email-container {
    background: #ffffff;
    width: 480px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: #222;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  a.reset-btn {
    background: #0077ff;
    color: white !important;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: inline-block;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,119,255,0.2);
  }
  a.reset-btn:hover {
    background: #005ec2;
  }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #999;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Tabster account.  
       Click the button below to set a new password.</p>
    <a href={{resetLink}} class="reset-btn">Reset Password</a>
    <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}} Tabster. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
